# SVX Guardian Roadmap

**SVX Guardian** is an open-source monitoring system designed for **SvxLink** radio nodes.

The project aims to provide a modern, modular and extensible platform capable of monitoring the health and status of a complete SvxLink installation, including EchoLink, Reflector services and the Raspberry Pi operating system.

---

# Project Goals

- Professional monitoring of SvxLink nodes
- Modern responsive web dashboard
- Multi-language user interface
- Telegram and e-mail notifications
- REST API
- Easy installation
- Open Source community project

---

